Value PORT (\S+)
Value LINK (\S+)
Value STATE (\S+)
Value DUPLEX (\S+)
Value SPEED (\S+)
Value TRUNK (\S+)
Value TAG (\S+)
Value PVID (\S+)
Value PRI (\d+)
Value MAC (\S+)
Value NAME (.*)

Start
  ^Port\s+Link\s+State -> Next
  ^${PORT}\s+${LINK}\s+${STATE}\s+${DUPLEX}\s+${SPEED}\s+${TRUNK}\s+${TAG}\s+${PVID}\s+${PRI}\s+${MAC}\s+${NAME} -> Record
